<p>Haha, I know just what you mean rvrags!</p><p>Trying to say anything about this stuff, this Looking and the nature of oneself, requires either no words or a deluge of words, and neither can really convey what it is that is trying to be conveyed.</p><p>Thanks,</p><p>Gerrit</p>
